Step 1 - Click security group on the left pane
Step 2 - Select SG - Edit inbound rules
Step 3 - Choose ELB Webserver
Step 4 - Choose web server for HTTP, HTTPS - my IP
Step 5 - Click save rule - view successfully modified
Step 6 - Open VSCode
Step 7 - Click instances
Step 8 - Click your running instances - click connect
Step 9 - Click on SSH client - Copy link below
Step 10 - Open VSCode and click terminal - View powershell
Step 11 - Copy the link path to your key pair
Step 12 - use sl - paste code -enter
Step 13 - Copy SSH
Step 14 - Paste ssh - Change root to ec2-user
Step 15 - Successful
